<center><font size=7><b>Tau Ceti 1</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 3</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Tips</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>Dock with supply centers as often as
possible and save the game to tape
after equipping. Travel at top speed if
you can, but if something starts
shooting at you, stop and shoot it
before you run into trouble. For
example, if Hunters
start shooting at you when you come
off a jump pod, don't run to the city,
'cos you'll probably run into a fortress
or something. Don't shoot at harmless
buildings or they won't let you dock.
Don't risk flying at night, just dock and
use the wait&nbsp;command a few times. If
you're going to use missiles against
Fortresses or Hunter mark III's, make
sure you're very close, so they can't
use their AMM's. Use the notepad to
keep a check on what reactor sub-stations
you've visited. Beware that
City up in the far North!!!
 <i>(Andrew Ostler in Your Sinclair issue 5)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite Shields</td><td>49784,201</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Missiles</td><td>49116,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Ammo</td><td>49207,167</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Flares</td><td>49161,167</td></tr>
</table>
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>With this neat little program you get infinite flares, infinite missiles and
infinite antimissiles
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<pre>
 10 CLS
 20 LET T=0: FOR N=60000 TO 60061: READ A
 30 LET T=T+A: POKE N,A: NEXT N
 40 IF T<>6245 THEN PRINT "CHECKSUM ERROR": STOP
 50 RANDOMIZE USR 60000
 60 DATA
221,33,0,236,17,200,0,62,35,55,205,86,5,48,241,62,201,50,13,236,33,136,234
 70 DATA
17,0,64,1,22,0,237,176,205,3,236,49,31,64,195,0,64,205,19,236,175,50,220,191
 80 DATA 50,53,192,50,54,192,50,7,192,50,8,192,195,0,91
</pre>
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
